</CO>
<LP>
   TORONTO -- CAE Industries Ltd. said its CAE Electronics
Ltd. unit has been awarded a 39 million Canadian dollar ($34
million) contract by Singapore Airlines to design and
manufacture flight simulators for the Airbus A-310 and Boeing
747-400 aircraft.
   The simulators will be delivered in the summer of 1992.
</LP>
