   AMERICAN BARRICK RESOURCES Corp. said it plans to sell
five million common shares for total proceeds of 122.5
million Canadian dollars (U.S.$106.8 million). The Toronto
gold mining concern said an underwriting group led by Gordon
Capital Corp. agreed to purchase the shares for C$24.50 each
