                         MORTGAGES
                                                                                                       

</LP>
<TEXT>
   Federal Home Loan Mortgage Corp. -- $500 million of real
estate mortgage investment conduit securities is being
offered in 10 classes by Prudential-Bache Securities. The
offering, FHLMC 194, is backed by Freddie Mac 8 1/2%
securities with a weighted average coupon rate of 9.40% and
weighted average remaining term to maturity of 25.67 years.
Details on prices and yields weren't immediately available.
                                                                                                       

